{
    "description": "VALIDATION-semantics parity cases (not resolution): each case carries its own inline `inputMap` that the client runs through its map validator (Frida `validateMap` / Xposed `:core` `MapLoader.validate`), asserting the schema-enforced constraints BOTH clients agree on. This closes the systemic gap that let resolution divergences through unnoticed. Pins, in both accept/reject directions, the constraints both core validators enforce: `schema_version` (const 3 hard gate), non-empty (`minLength: 1`) `obfuscated` (class/method/field), non-empty method `signature` and field `type`, non-empty `version` AND whitespace-only `version` rejection, `app` dotted-package pattern, `version_code` width (accept 2^32 = 4294967296, reject 2^53 = 9007199254740992 — xposed#8/f8 boundary) AND `version_code` lower bound (reject negative), and the reserved record keys (`__proto__`, `constructor`, `prototype`). NOTE: two constraints are intentionally NOT pinned here and are delegated to rosetta-maps `schema/samples/`: (1) `signer_sha256`'s `^[0-9a-f]{64}$` regex, because the Xposed `:core` `MapLoader.validate` does not check it (only the full schema and the Frida Zod / Xposed `SignerGuard` paths do) — pinned by `schema/samples/{valid,invalid}/*signer*`; and (2) `additionalProperties:false` / unknown-key rejection, because the Kotlin `validate` harness decodes `inputMap` with `ignoreUnknownKeys=true`, so a stray key is dropped at decode and never reaches `validate` — it cannot be expressed through this validate harness, and is instead pinned by the rosetta-maps `schema/samples/invalid/unknown-*-key.json` samples (the same delegation already given to `signer_sha256`). Provider-neutral; see README.md.",
    "cases": [
        {
            "name": "a well-formed minimal map validates (baseline)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa"
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectValid": true
        },
        {
            "name": "empty class obfuscated is rejected (minLength:1)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": ""
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
            "name": "empty method obfuscated is rejected (minLength:1)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa",
                        "methods": {
                            "bar": {
                                "obfuscated": "",
                                "signature": "()V"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
            "name": "empty field obfuscated is rejected (minLength:1)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa",
                        "fields": {
                            "baz": {
                                "obfuscated": "",
                                "type": "I"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
            "name": "wrong schema_version is rejected (hard gate on 3)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 2,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa"
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
            "name": "a 2^32 version_code validates (longVersionCode, not int32-masked: xposed#8/f8 accept)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 4294967296,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa"
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectValid": true
        },
        {
            "name": "a 2^53 version_code is rejected (over Number.MAX_SAFE_INTEGER: xposed#8/f8 reject)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 9007199254740992,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa"
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
            "name": "an empty version label is rejected (minLength:1)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "com.example.app",
                "version": "",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa"
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
            "name": "a non-dotted app id is rejected (package-name pattern)",
            "kind": "validate",
            "inputMap": {
                "schema_version": 3,
                "app": "not a package name",
                "version": "1.0.0",
                "version_code": 100,
                "classes": {
                    "com.example.app.Foo": {
                        "obfuscated": "aaaa"
                    }
                }
            },
            "expectError": "MapValidation"
        },
        {
